io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.properties

Class ObjectDBPropertyStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zoodb.api.impl.ZooPC
      • io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.objectdb.DbObject
        • io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.objectdb.LongObject
          • io.github.bigbio.pgatk.io.properties.ObjectDBPropertyStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ObjectDBPropertyStorage
extends LongObject
    This class interacts with the back-end database to manage identification objects. Interacting with the back-end database might cause InterruptedException. These exceptions are passed as runtime exceptions for methods returning identification objects.
    Author:
    ypriverol
    See Also:
